high_descs: Move to the opposite corner of the room to the right side of the TV stand facing the phone
Pick up on phone sitting on the right side of the TV stand
Carry the phone to the coffee table on the side by the statues
Place the phone on the blue plate on top of the coffee table by the statues
Pick up the plate with the phone on top of it
Carry the plate with the phone on it to the black side table next to the couch
Place the plate with the phone on it on top of the left side of the black side table
anns.task_desc: Move a plate with a plate on it to the black end table

high_descs: Take two steps forward, then turn right and walk to the end of the couch, then turn left and walk across the room, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the cell phone that is underneath the television on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the end of the coffee table, then turn right to face the table.
Place the cell phone on the blue plate that is on the table.
Pick up the blue plate with the cell phone on it.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left again and take three steps, then turn to the left to face the black table.
Place the plate with the cell phone on it on the table.
anns.task_desc: To put the plate and cell phone on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go past the couch. Then turn left to face the slim side of the TV.
Pick up the cell phone from under the TV.
Take the cell phone and turn left, then right past the couch and turn right to face the coffee table.
Place the cell phone on the plate on the left side of the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Carry the plate and turn around to see the black end table beside the couch.
Place the plate and cell phone on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Move a cell phone and plate to a table.
